  <summary>Deductive Zebra Puzzle Logic Game</summary>
  <developer_name>Tim Charper</developer_name>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>

  <description>
    <p>
      EmojiClu is a graphical implementation of the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zebra_Puzzle">Zebra Puzzle</a>, built with GTK.
    </p>
    <p>
      EmojiClu takes pretty heavy inspiration by <a
      href="https://www.kaser.com/home.html">Everett Kaser's Sherlock</a>. The
      creator of this game has played 1,000s of hours of Everett's game over the
      decades. My grandparents played Kaser's game, my parents still play it,
      and so do I. Puzzle generator aims to be more difficult than Kaser's game.
    </p>
  </description>

